## 1. 问题复现

采用jsonrpc协议，当Provider侧比Consumer侧字段多时，会导致反序列化失败，报UnrecognizedPropertyException。

## 2. 单元测试

```java
import com.fasterxml.jackson.core.JsonProcessingException;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationFeature;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.exc.UnrecognizedPropertyException;
import lombok.Data;
import org.junit.Before;
import org.junit.Test;

public class TestUnrecognizedFeld {

    private String json;

    @Before
    public void setUp() {
        this.json = "{\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"klz\", \"job\": \"it\"}";
    }

    @Test(expected = UnrecognizedPropertyException.class)
    public void beforeFix() throws JsonProcessingException {
        ObjectMapper objectMapper = new ObjectMapper();
        objectMapper.readValue(json, User.class);
    }

    @Test
    public void afterFix() throws JsonProcessingException {
        ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
        mapper.configure(DeserializationFeature.FAIL_ON_UNKNOWN_PROPERTIES, false);
        mapper.readValue(json, User.class);
    }

    @Data
    public static class User {
        
        private Long id;
        private String name;
        
    }
    
}
```

> 上述单元测试依赖于：lombok、junit4、dubbo这3个包。

